{"tid":1810974,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"每過一排就聽一隻新碟","createTime":"2020-01-04T10:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T13:07:17.000Z","uid":345177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1984f68ca1f1b21cde5fcc5046fa3fbe8d2db28","tid":1810974,"uid":345177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"紀錄下自已聽過咩碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜都聽 , 舊碟新碟 Jazz Rock Rap 咩都試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4929a3e7934be1b9b4de4c7303f3351f93a22156","tid":1810974,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"咁你最近聽左咩"},{"pid":"d609ee194060487f74b8cb0ae178535fd311a9f2","tid":1810974,"uid":112523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7TML_MTQdg4&amp;t=363s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7TML_MTQdg4%26t%3D363s&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=0ed2f8f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7TML_MTQdg4&amp;t=363s</a>"},{"pid":"3f42c99c97752ed1eefdb1148ce80243856e395f","tid":1810974,"uid":345177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLx4FLy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLx4FLy.jpg&h=bdd215d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSwans - Leaving Meaning  <span style=\"color: red;\">7/10</span><br />\n<br />\n老牌Industrial / No Wave / Noise rock band <br />\n<br />\n覺得呢隻碟冇Swans早期小小既碟咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 與其話係新既Idea, 不如話呢隻碟係base on 舊既諗法再創作 <br />\n<br />\n近年Swans最好既碟應該係To Be Kind , Leaving Meaning 似To Be Kind 既Ambient + Noise版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Swans應有既原素都有,但爭緊D 驚喜同埋Michael Gira 既憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdd06cf95cc71630ee488482da42ce8db83fbe3","tid":1810974,"uid":345177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4929a3e7934be1b9b4de4c7303f3351f93a22156","tid":1810974,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"咁你最近聽左咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"岩岩去左打機未打完個review<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745b55e599d160991afd3d19b681f79e65c77ba9","tid":1810974,"uid":345177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T20:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PtzLPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PtzLPA.jpg&h=7196ec8a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcbQ3Do.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcbQ3Do.jpg&h=e04fc2db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJWksPWDKOc&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwJWksPWDKOc%26t%3D1s&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=111e72ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJWksPWDKOc&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<strong>The Caretakers - Everywhere at the End of Time - Stage 6 / An Empty Bliss Beyond This World</strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">9/10</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">Ambient/ Drones/ Turntable Music/Lofi</span><br />\n<br />\n個人聽得算多唔同Ambient既碟,覺得好多隻都有唔同既特色<br />\n<br />\neg Brian Eno 係好Relax ,,, Grouper既係好Sentimental .. Aphex Twins 既就好技術性 + 10/10既Acid電子聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Caretakers 早期小小既An Empty Bliss Beyond This World已經好唔同 , 呢隻碟將舊既Ballroom music remix再剪剪貼貼做Ambient Music<br />\n<br />\n感覺上係好有懷舊同埋懷念既感覺 , 係有小小會令人唔開心既&quot;Ambient&quot;<br />\n係一種好獨特好神奇既Ambient, 咁當然亦都係好舒服既Ambient<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Caretakers後期小小既Everywhere at the End of Time Stage 1 ~ 6感覺上係同 An Empty Bliss Beyond This World有感覺上既唔同<br />\n<br />\nBallroom music  開始模糊, 變左既係一堆White Noise + 空靈既聲音溝埋 , 將Caretakers 變成一種好Spiritual/憤怒/ 哲學性 既Ambient<br />\n<br />\n六個鐘既音樂好成功咁將一個心理狀態刻畫左出黎, 我覺得Ambient 界Caretakers絕對係獨特中既獨特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc4b270d5ea6c3275dfd5bcd1cbf7bf446fc49a","tid":1810974,"uid":345177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T20:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqey1us.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiqey1us.jpg&h=3a13ef31&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Ornett Coleman - Change of the Century</strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">8/10</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">Avant Garde Jazz</span><br />\n<br />\nJazz好多人都聽過,但認真去接觸既人未必好多<br />\n<br />\nJazz 大師入面Miles Davis / Charles Mingus / John Coltrane 既Jazz Albums 係頂級既作品 , 特別係Miles Davis 既Kind of blue 不但只係劃時代既作品 , 仲係改變Jazz 既一張巨作<br />\n<br />\nOrnett Coleman 可能冇上面果幾位大師咁出名 (但其實都好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但Ornett Coleman Avant Garde / Free Jazz 既推動絕對唔可以睇小<br />\n<br />\n講到Avant Garde / Free Jazz 可能有部份人會首先諗起John Coltrane / Charles Mingus中後期既作品 , 但其實Ornett Coleman 早係The Shape of Jazz to Come已經實驗Jazz 既自由度<br />\n<br />\nChange of the century 更加係將Avant Garde Jazz變得更加成熟 , 自由既停頓 , 新式既Progression , 不重於架構既Jazz , Change of the Century都可以聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯一要Complain 既係隻碟可能聽一兩次就會返去聽返Miles Davis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eb69dc787b97bfd1a2c15d33d921f3a0fee327","tid":1810974,"uid":345177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實個po都係諗住比自已做下紀錄,寫返自已感受,大家有興趣先交流下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"96bc06462efc136d907499954aed40c47599be77","tid":1810974,"uid":206554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"Young Thug - So much fun"}]}